Title: زفة عريس في بلدة الجلمة
AltTitle.other: A Zaffeh in al-jalameh Village. Zaffeh is a ceremony before the actual wedding where friends and relatives of the groom gather to dance
Description.note: During the Zaffeh of Mohamamd Abu Farha's cousin; with the presence of the traditional poet Abu Bassam al-Jilmawi.
